# Documentation

This folder contains generated documentation and analysis outputs.

## Contents

- `myr_sgd_analysis.png` - Generated analysis plots from main.py
- Additional plots and charts generated by the analysis scripts

## Auto-Generated Content

Most files in this folder are automatically generated by running the analysis scripts. Do not edit manually - regenerate by running the appropriate script.

## Usage

These files are useful for:
- Presentations and reports
- Quick visual reference
- Sharing analysis results

## Regeneration

To regenerate documentation:
```bash
python src/main.py  # Generates main analysis plots
python src/backtest.py  # Generates backtesting visualizations
```
